<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>John Legend has been handling more of the grocery shopping duties lately for the Legend and Teigen household. </p>

<p>And the EGOT holder, 41, cut a stylish look as he tackled the grocery shopping on Tuesday with his children and the help of a nanny. </p>

<p>John (born John Stephens) wore white jeans, with a light wash denim jacket and a colorful patterned button-up top as he headed to the store in Beverly Hills.  </p>

