<p>The All of Me hitmaker teamed his look with white lace-up sneakers and a black reusable face mask. </p>

<p>His son and daughter, who he shares with wife Chrissy Teigen, rode in the grocery basket on the group's way out of the store. </p>

<p>Luna, four, was spotted holding a large bouquet of pink roses likely for her model mom who was at home and is currently expecting the couple's third child. </p>

